gration of Trex Reveal® and Trex Wedge® lighting systems for 5-Star nighttime aesthetics in Loudoun and Fairfax."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"className":"ServiceInclusions-module__sDDdhG__card","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"ServiceInclusions-module__sDDdhG__iconWrapper","children":["$","svg",null,{"width":"24","height":"24","viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"3","strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","children":["$","polyline",null,{"points":"20 6 9 17 4 12"}]}]}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"ServiceInclusions-module__sDDdhG__itemTitle","children":"Pro-Solar® Post Caps"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"ServiceInclusions-module__sDDdhG__itemDesc","children":"Adding custom solar or wired post caps to your Trex railing for enhanced safety and beauty across Arlington and Stafford."}]]}]]}]]}]]}]}]
